WEBVTT

00:03:29.550 --> 00:03:31.770
Alexa, introduce yourself.

00:03:32.570 --> 00:03:34.760
Alexa: I am Alexa and I am
designed around your voice.

00:03:35.130 --> 00:03:39.410
I can provide information, 
music, news, weather and more.

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:42.840
AR: She listens to me,
and understands me, too.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:44.200
Have a look.

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:47.310
Alexa, could you 
wake me up in the morning?

00:03:48.190 --> 00:03:49.610
Alexa: Alarm, for what time?

00:03:51.070 --> 00:03:52.450
AR: How about 7 o'clock?

00:03:53.300 --> 00:03:55.120
Alexa: Alarm set for 7am.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.520
ARL I only asked her to wake me up,

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:00.040
not to set an alarm,